 to test-drive macOS 15.2 before public release, sign up for the Apple Beta Software Program at \u003ca href=\"https://beta.apple.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebeta.apple.com\u003c/a\u003e for free using only your Apple ID. You\u0026#39;ll need to follow the link to enroll your Mac, enabling the computer to receive macOS betas via Apple\u0026#39;s standard Software Update mechanism.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSource: \u003ca href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2024/11/04/macos-sequoia-15-2-menu-bar-weather/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMacRumors\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
